{"tid":1922255,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"點解宜家啲game咁灰","createTime":"2020-03-12T12:44:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T04:15:44.000Z","uid":352066,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a98d84d8c0399cd561903de43bccd142386d9213","tid":1922255,"uid":352066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:44:28.000Z","msg":"喱個係我已經有5年的疑惑，都積咗唔少怨氣 &mdash;&mdash; 點解宜家啲game咁灰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次發現呢個問題係5年前玩緊神魔之塔，早期角色是這樣的。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KBSx0Rj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKBSx0Rj.png&h=810b38cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0nZwwXZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0nZwwXZ.png&h=6f4c4900&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Yz09KF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Yz09KF.png&h=d582973b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後期唔知係咪換咗插畫師<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s7FGUbF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs7FGUbF.png&h=2650f017&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oD9AebG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoD9AebG.png&h=771b1b7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mY6u242.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmY6u242.png&h=314984a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解啲嘢好似deep-fried 咗咁，大家好似打晒白燈，我淨係見到一大堆藍一大堆綠，啲<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃</span>變晒<span style=\"color: brown;\">啡</span>色。<br />\n<br />\n玩第二個遊戲&mdash; LOL，佢哋喜歡更新啲角色，大家睇吓新舊對比：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bkJ1UjX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbkJ1UjX.jpg&h=f234ffa9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BeidLrC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBeidLrC.jpg&h=4e829499&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ppacgyi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fppacgyi.jpg&h=df7b7a50&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SOohsEY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSOohsEY.jpg&h=e7ea0a3a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UC44R6E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUC44R6E.jpg&h=f87afa0c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3PMVYME.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3PMVYME.jpg&h=bee5c6e4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W83Jodk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW83Jodk.jpg&h=b1b07de0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ti7qByk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fti7qByk.jpg&h=3bc81476&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">佢係咪畫得差？完全唔係。</span>但我遠遠會覺得舊版個顏色比新版好。<br />\n<br />\n我得出一個結論：今時今日啲人好鍾意用realistic方法去上金銀銅色，而錯就錯係呢一點到&mdash;&mdash; 係暗色嗰度落一大堆<span style=\"color: brown;\">啡</span>色。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rFBVYQo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrFBVYQo.jpg&h=2667f9ee&s={SIZE}\" />同時，畫人時候個肉色，因為想打陰影，又用<span style=\"color: brown;\">啡</span>色去做暗色。<span style=\"color: red;\">啡色襯啡色，即死。</span><br />\n<br />\nSolution: <br />\n好多設計緊嘅game應該要考慮下呢啲問題，例如：<br />\n- 小心啲用暗+飽和度高嘅顏色<br />\n- 唔好再用灰色做底色畫畫<br />\n- 你個金銀銅色一又想玩反光，加環境色入去，你小心啲變透明，成個盔甲同背景色一樣。<br />\n<br />\n寫住咁多先，睇下使唔使續文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f70cc2386deca87d8f0216964259d6626def48b5","tid":1922255,"uid":29080,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:46:13.000Z","msg":"以為你講啲故事灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d981b822b1743f3fec8894f9c52e5c2b4ab089